Deploy React app

Step 1 : Use command npm run build to check all error


Step 2 : go to vercel.com , login use github, Click on Add button and select Project


Step 3 : select github repo 

Step 4 : Choose framework as create-react-app


Step 5 : Select root directory

Step 6 : Click on Deploy